data.description:
Welcome to downtown living at its finest! This stunning studio apartment in the heart of the garment district at 700 Broadway Boulevard Unit #203, Kansas City, MO 64105 offers an unparalleled urban living experience.

Upon entering, you are greeted by a spacious open-concept layout with a flood of natural light pouring in through the giant west-facing windows. The studio features a full bath and is meticulously designed to maximize space and functionality, making it the perfect urban retreat.

The building boasts an array of amenities, including a storage unit, fitness center, club room, movie room, business center, and laundry room. Additionally, residents will enjoy the convenience of trash, water, and snow removal services included. The property is also wired for Google Fiber, ensuring seamless connectivity for all your digital needs.

Situated in the vibrant garment district and river market area, this location offers easy access to the streetcar and nearby attractions. With easy highway access and parking available for rent near the building, commuting and exploring the city is a breeze.

Don't miss this opportunity to immerse yourself in the dynamic energy of downtown Kansas City while enjoying the comfort and convenience of modern urban living. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of downtown living!
